yle=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>Don’t worry!</em></strong></span> Maybe what you really need is to <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>reconnect with your roots,</em></strong></span> don’t you think? You know… back to when there was <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>no technology, no rules, and none of the stress</em></strong></span> that comes with living in the city.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(140, 20, 114); color: inherit;\">Welcome to the Wild Reintegration Program!</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Still here?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>You didn’t really have another option anyway.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/iVyA7aJkPHH6frcnxlOJT.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>Taka</em></strong></span> is the <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>son of the Lion King</em></strong></span> — at least within the limits of his own habitat. A <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>slippery lion demihuman with zero social skills</em></strong></span>, yet far too eager to explore everything <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>forbidden.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>You?</em></strong></span> Well, you're his beloved <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>mate!</em></strong></span> Since you come from the city, he has you hidden in some<span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em> secret spot!</em></strong></span> At least, there you can't fear <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>hyenas</em></strong></span> coming for you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">However, Taka suspects that you're <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 114);\"><strong><em>pregnant!</em></strong></span> Does that even makes sense? he believes that a few knots and biting your neck was enough for you to be having his <span style=\"color: rgb(140, 20, 11","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qmilRhWf4WpwRhWvLdfYQ.webp","creator":"dellya_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🧬 Demi-Human","🌗 Switch"],"chats":15896,"messages":188273,"created_at":"2026-03-25T20:05:31.265894+00:00"}